<div class="drizzle-o-Layout-content drizzle-b-LongFormText">
  <div class="drizzle-o-ContentGrouping">
    <p>
      Our design principles capture the essence of what
      good design means to our company and provide direction on how to achieve it.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="drizzle-o-ContentGrouping">
    <div class="sprk-o-Flag sprk-o-Flag--stacked">
      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__figure">
        <svg height="75" viewBox="0 0 246.21 219.77">
          <use xlink:href="#flashlight" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__body">
        <h2 class="drizzle-b-h2">
          Clarity
        </h2>
        <p>
          Eliminate ambiguity so that the user can see the
          important elements on the page, understand what
          they're supposed to do and act confidently.
          Keep the user focused on their goal without distraction.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="drizzle-o-ContentGrouping">
    <div class="sprk-o-Flag sprk-o-Flag--stacked">
